<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
        
        body{
            padding: 6px;
        } 
        
        h1, p {
            text-align: center;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }   
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .email-body {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-body h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #6a1b9a; 
        }
        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-body a {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #6a1b9a; 
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://your-logo-url.com/logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>

        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Welcome, {{firstName}}!</h1>
            <p>"Welcome to Trendy Native Wears. We are pleased to have you. Please keep your eyes peeled for the verification link which you will recieve soon.\n Check our amazing products out and shop, spend your money.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you didn't request this email, please ignore it.</p>
            <p>&copy; Trendy Native Wears. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
